---
---

<section class="social-proof rx">
  <div class="w">
    <div class="proof-header">
      <span class="proof-eyebrow">What Clients Say</span>
      <h2 class="proof-title">Law Firms That Fixed Their Marketing</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial rxl d1">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"We wasted $200K on ads we couldn't track. After Joe's analysis, we knew exactly which channels brought retained clients. We cut waste and increased revenue."</p>
        <div class="attribution">
          <div class="attr-name">Sarah Martinez</div>
          <div class="attr-firm">Managing Partner, Personal Injury Firm</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial rxl d2">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"Our intake was losing 40% of leads between form and consultation. The workflow redesign and CRM integration fixed it. 27% more cases in 6 months."</p>
        <div class="attribution">
          <div class="attr-name">Marcus Chen</div>
          <div class="attr-firm">Operations Director, Family Law Practice</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial rxr d1">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"We finally have a marketing strategy instead of just responding to vendor pitches. It's coordinated. It's measurable. Results are 3x better."</p>
        <div class="attribution">
          <div class="attr-name">James Rodriguez</div>
          <div class="attr-firm">Managing Director, Business Law Group</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial rxr d2">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"Hiring three marketing firms and getting no accountability. Joe unified them on one metric: cost per retained client. Game changer for us."</p>
        <div class="attribution">
          <div class="attr-name">Jennifer Park</div>
          <div class="attr-firm">Managing Partner, Litigation Boutique</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .social-proof {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #FAFAF5 100%);
  }

  .proof-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .proof-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .proof-title {
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 56px);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .testimonial {
    padding: 32px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.1);
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .testimonial:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.1);
  }

  .stars {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .quote {
    font-family: var(--bas);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .attribution {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.1);
    padding-top: 16px;
  }

  .attr-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .attr-firm {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--dim);
  }
</style>
